h1 Forgot my password
p Enter your email so we find your password....

hr
form.form-horizontal(ng-submit="forgotPassword()", name="forgotPasswordForm", role="form")
    .form-group
        label.control-label.col-sm-2(for="emailAddress") Email
        .col-sm-10
            input.form-control(type="text", data-ng-model="emailAddress", placeholder="Email", name="emailAddress", required, autofocus)
    .form-group
        .col-sm-offset-2.col-sm-10
            button.btn.btn-default(type="submit", data-ng-disabled="forgotPasswordForm.$invalid") Email me my password
hr